product_name: Red Gold Tomato Ketchup, 32 Ounce Bottle (Pack of 12)
description: Twelve (12) 32oz. bottles of Red Gold Tomato Ketchup. Real ketchup, free of artificial colors, flavors or preservatives. Full-bodied ketchup, true tomato flavor. No-drip flip-top ketchup bottle makes one-handed dispensing a breeze. Red Gold tomatoes are family-grown, family-owned and family-made since 1942.
